        <body>
            <div1 xml:id="d001" type="work" decls="#md" met="E">
                <head>
                    <title>1</title>
                    <bibl source="digital">Barbara Zlobec</bibl>
                </head>
                <l xml:id="d001l1" n="1">Barbara gens italos venit eversura penates:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l2" n="2">Et magnum a gelido panditur axe malum:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l3" n="3">Venit et illa die saevo cum Cerva Leoni</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l4" n="4">Cum secura Lupo conseret Agna latus;</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l5" n="5">Impia cessabunt tandem et civilia bella:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l6" n="6">In foribus cum iam fortior hostis erit.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l7" n="7">Non petiit tantus nostras exercitus oras</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l8" n="8">Intulit Ausoniae cum ferus arma Getes:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l9" n="9">Nec cum Romanum properaret perdere nomen</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l10" n="10">Annibal aut celsa gallus ab alpe ruens:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l11" n="11">Vix avium tantas emittit bruma catervas:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l12" n="12">Cum mutata novo frigore torpet hyems:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l13" n="13">Vix frondes tot sylva gerit, vix littus harenas</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l14" n="14">Ionii tot habet Carpathiique maris:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l15" n="15">Iam video totos impleri milite campos:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l16" n="16">Et pelagus structis classibus omne tegi.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l17" n="17">Iam trepidare nova video formidine terras:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l18" n="18">Atque quati turres et tremere omne solum:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l19" n="19">Heu quantas strages, heu quantas cerno rovinas:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l20" n="20">Iam tollent pulvis telaque missa diem:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l21" n="21">Iamque sagittarum densa pugnabitur umbra.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l22" n="22">Letiferi tantus missilis imber adest.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l23" n="23">Captivos pueros, captivas cerno puellas:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l24" n="24">Et captivorum ferrea vincla pedum:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l25" n="25">Ignibus incendi sacras hostilibus aedes,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l26" n="26">Deque sinu matrum pignora parva trahi.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l27" n="27">Sanguine torrentes, decurrent sanguine valles,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l28" n="28">Usque adeo rabies Martis ira furit:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l29" n="29">Scilicet Ausonios nunque diffusa per agros</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l30" n="30">Huic par tempestas diluviumque fuit.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l31" n="31">Foelices illi quibus has ne cernere clades,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l32" n="32">Neve pati possent, contingit ante mori:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l33" n="33">O patria o tellus olim invictissima tu nunc</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l34" n="34">Heu facinus, cunctis obvia praeda iaces.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l35" n="35">Ve tibi quae septem claudis munimine colles:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l36" n="36">Et genus a Troia principiumque trahis:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l37" n="37">Ve tibi desidia nimium luxuque fluenti:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l38" n="38">Ve tibi ter miserae, ve tibi Roma quater.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l39" n="39">Hesperiae gentes civilia ponite bella:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l40" n="40">Et tantum a nobis hoc prohibete nefas,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l41" n="41">Et vos o Veneti gentis tutela latinae;</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l42" n="42">In quibus Europae est tota reposta salus:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l43" n="43">Consulite in medium et vestras effundite vires:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l44" n="44">Non aberit caeptis talibus ipse deus.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l45" n="45">Quid facis in tanto, Pastor Romane, periclo?</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l46" n="46">Sollicitum totos quem decet esse dies:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l47" n="47">Nonne vides quot regna ferox invaserit hostis,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l48" n="48">Nonne vides nostrae quantum minuantur opes;</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l49" n="49">Ut vigil incolumes populos tueris et urbes</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l50" n="50">Cervici imposita est sarcina magna tuae.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l51" n="51">Summe deus qui celsa colis fastigia coeli;</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l52" n="52">Quo sine nec vires arma nec ulla valent:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l53" n="53">Aspice nos, hostemque precor confunde furentem,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l54" n="54">Qui cladem Latio pernitiemque parat.</l>
                <lb/>
                <lb/>
            </div1>
